Class MainCli

java.lang.Object
com.umidity.cli.frames.FrameManager
com.umidity.cli.MainCli
All Implemented Interfaces:
InputFormListener
public class MainCli
extends FrameManager
implements InputFormListener
This is the main FrameManager for the CLI version of Umidity.
The CLI version is still under development and therefore still not much optimized nor well documented.
